## 🎯 **Key Takeaways from Real Interviews:**

1. **ROW_NUMBER vs RANK vs DENSE_RANK** is asked in **every single company** (Stripe, Google, Amazon, Myntra, Deloitte, Capgemini) [[9]], [[10]], [[12]], [[21]]

